<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h3 class="h2-heading-ss">
      Checking the 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        hardware and details
      </span>
    </h3>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width">
      When it comes to authenticating a Louis Vuitton handbag, the hardware and details are crucial. Here are some key things to look for:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-start">
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         The hardware on an authentic Louis Vuitton handbag is made of high-quality metal, such as brass or gold-tone metal. This ensures durability and a luxurious finish that stands the test of time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The zippers, buckles, and other metal components should be heavy and have a smooth, even finish. Authentic Louis Vuitton hardware feels substantial and operates smoothly, reflecting the brand’s commitment to exceptional quality.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The Louis Vuitton logo should be engraved on the hardware, and the font should be consistent with the brand’s signature style. Any deviation in the font or engraving quality can be a red flag.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The stitching on the hardware should be precise and even, with no loose threads or uneven stitches. This attention to detail is a hallmark of Louis Vuitton’s craftsmanship.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The hardware should be securely attached to the bag, with no signs of wear or damage. Loose or poorly attached hardware is a clear indicator of a counterfeit item.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Three text columns",
    "class": "article_columns article_three-columns article_three-text-columns rebranding-wider-section-top-only",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}